{"tid":2500481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大角咀Hoxeland 黃店就可以比屎你食？","createTime":"2021-04-22T16:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T17:31:20.000Z","uid":355041,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bb738d17a76559c5f4fe89e47a543bd8bae2d37a","tid":2500481,"uid":355041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"大角咀Homxland<br />\n<br />\n勁多人推介但食物質素同服務真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要收得唔平。叫左明太子海鮮薄餅（$118）同西班牙海鮮炒飯（$168），另加一。個薄餅仲薄過餅乾，完全冇焗過咁，海鮮料算足但好乾身，料同餅底分離，面頭放一堆配料一路食一路跌，不如分開上啦。到個炒飯，嚴格黎講係食緊飯焦，每粒飯咬落去脆身同乾硬，熱度欠奉，仲有好多粒黑色一粒粒唔知咩既肉，個大蝦過份乾身，似蝦乾，其他既料都過乾，冇炒既感覺。諗住服務搭夠？錯啦！個阿姐收碟速度其快，驚死你hold住佢d碟，最搞鬼係佢收碟唔會幫你清埋枱面。收錢又急急腳咁催你幾轉。<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解可以冇人劣評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人講就我講。不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者親身求證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29099ba32cfa2ddef03ae7e30fa418968f83597","tid":2500481,"uid":172733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"呢間野真係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n比周庭佢地吹奏完勁多人去<br />\n<br />\n我都未撚食過有餐廳連牛脷都可以整得難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8dceb406f3ffe0d1bb9daa70eb3c38d4852ec16","tid":2500481,"uid":387391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"有冇圖先"},{"pid":"b3ad2b6c9014e186db6185b13f1421b2f1df72eb","tid":2500481,"uid":6352,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"黃店水平不嬲參差"},{"pid":"5fa05214dcb4be159d47370d0257091a1de8ed08","tid":2500481,"uid":355041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8dceb406f3ffe0d1bb9daa70eb3c38d4852ec16","tid":2500481,"uid":387391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci